      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Teste de Resistência de Força: CD 19, one Large or smaller creature Agarrado by the remorhaz (it can have up to two creatures swallowed at a time). O alvo is swallowed by the remorhaz, and a condição Agarrado ends. A swallowed creature has the Cego and Impedido conditions, it has Total Cover against attacks and other effects outside the remorhaz, and it takes 10 (3d6) dano de ácido mais 10 (3d6) dano de fogo at the start of each of the remorhaz's turns.\nIf the remorhaz takes 30 de dano or more on a single turn from uma criatura inside it, the remorhaz must succeed on a CD 15 Constituição saving throw at the end of that turn or regurgitate all swallowed creatures, each of which falls in a space within 1,5 m of the remorhaz and fica com a condição Caído. If the remorhaz dies, any swallowed creature no longer fica com a condição Impedido and can escape from the corpse by using 4,5 m of movement, exiting Caído.</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
